item.description:
Another pick-up game at the Lawrence YMCA. This game is for Yankee C- and above level. Players should be familiar with how to play 6-2 and 5-1 formations.

Please message me to get on the roster. If you have not played in my meetups recently, please mention the level of your play and confirm that you can play formations. If your name is not on the roster, you are not guaranteed a spot to play.

The meetup is free and YMCA membership is not required. There is plenty of parking at the lot behind the building and on the street next to the Y. When you enter, look for the big gym upstairs.

Best,

Katya
item.name: Lawrence High Intermediate Indoor Volleyball
